Wonderful. Thanks for sharing, Frank.

1227
01:15:14,093 --> 01:15:17,930
Okay. Now, I think we go to Roger.

1228
01:15:18,097 --> 01:15:21,517
Um, I actually have some things
I'd like to talk about if...

1229
