01:18:19,320 --> 01:18:22,281
that I was gonna do
whatever it took...

1285
01:18:22,781 --> 01:18:24,949
because I loved my brother...

1286
01:18:25,117 --> 01:18:29,454
and I was always gonna be there
for my brother. And I have been.

1287
01:18:29,622 --> 01:18:31,373
And you know what?

1288
01:18:31,540 --> 01:18:33,917
You can be too.

