01:21:22,211 --> 01:21:24,463
- Hey, Annette, how you doing?
- Fred.

1317
01:21:24,671 --> 01:21:28,466
Nick, I think we're gonna make it. I got
elves in the Workshop making presents.

1318
01:21:28,634 --> 01:21:30,927
